org.apache.distributedlog.metadata

Interface MetadataUpdater

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DryrunLogSegmentMetadataStoreUpdater, LogSegmentMetadataStoreUpdater

    public interface MetadataUpdater
    An updater to update metadata. It contains utility functions on mutating metadata.

      • setLogSegmentTruncated

        LogSegmentMetadata setLogSegmentTruncated(org.apache.distributedlog.util.Transaction<Object> txn,
                                          LogSegmentMetadata segment)
        Change the truncation status of a log segment to truncated. The operation won't be executed immediately. The update only happens after Transaction.execute().
        Parameters:
        txn - transaction used to set the log segment status
        segment - segment to set truncation status to truncated
        Returns:
        log segment that truncation status is set to truncated.
